query:
SELECT p.id, p.name, p.slug, p.regularPrice, p.categoryId, p.status, pi.url as imageUrl
FROM products p
LEFT JOIN product_images pi ON p.id = pi.productId AND pi.isPrimary = TRUE
WHERE p.categoryId = 1
ORDER BY p.id DESC
LIMIT 5;
